{"tid":351872,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(無粗口國家)台灣一名男子因行車糾紛向對方豎起中指　被判決侮辱罪","createTime":"2017-08-08T11:37:16.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-09T02:34:37.000Z","uid":100680,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"45e7e08e347b1cafc3fda49b11c1e1d328ac8da6","tid":351872,"uid":100680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T11:37:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20170727/640_8a36f1951733b7c1073838ffa1eecde5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20170727%2F640_8a36f1951733b7c1073838ffa1eecde5.jpg&h=6bb91302&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n桃園一名紀姓男子（27歲）今年4月25日上午8時許開車行經國道二號南桃園交流道附近路段時，因與姚姓男駕駛人發生行車糾紛而心生不滿，竟在諸多車輛來往頻繁的道路上對姚男比中指，整個過程被姚車上的行車記錄器錄下，經姚男提告後，桃園地檢署今依公然侮辱罪嫌將他聲請簡易判決處刑。（突發中心張沛森／桃園報導）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/new/20170727/1169483/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.appledaily.com.tw%2Frealtimenews%2Farticle%2Fnew%2F20170727%2F1169483%2F&d=wAxuK3IIaKUC0PTKA8tUdU%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=2f4cfda3\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/new/20170727/1169483/</a>"},{"pid":"ed1c93f15efe5f1836b7e6c26fbd054b9fb9fcf2","tid":351872,"uid":100680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T02:30:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5dd1c73c3840025bd87c23a4bb137a69a518a759","tid":351872,"uid":53223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T02:34:37.000Z","msg":"有強權冇公理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}